<h1 id="issues">Reporting issues</h1>
<ul>
  <li>
    Create a ticket in the appropriate sub-repository.
  </li>
  <li>
    Please always provide clear and concise information about
    <ol>
      <li>what you did,</li>
      <li>what you have expected and</li>
      <li>what the actual result/behaviour was</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li>
    If you think the issue is a security issue explain clearly why.
  </li>
  <li>
    Avoid to send confidential information (e.g. mask passwords).
  </li>
  <li>
    If you want to submit confidential information you can send personal
    e-mail to <a href="michael@stroeder.com">michael@stroeder.com</a>
    (<a href="https://stroeder.com/michael_at_stroeder.com-6A8BC938.asc">GPG key 6A8BC938</a>).
  </li>
</ul>

<h1 id="contrib">Contributions</h1>
<ul>
  <li>
    Create a ticket in the appropriate sub-repository.
  </li>
  <li>
    If you want to provide a solution create a pull-request.
  </li>
  <li>
    Explicitly agree to license of sub-project (mostly Apache-2.0)
    by adding a comment in the pull request.
  </li>
</ul>

